original_title: All Time Low - It’s Still Nothing Personal
overview: “10 years after first releasing 'Nothing Personal', we returned to Red Bull Studios in LA to revisit the making of the album. ‘It's Still Nothing Personal: A Ten Year Tribute' features all new recordings of the classic album. While we were there, we filmed the entire recording process and checked in with a few familar faces for a documentary about the album.”
title: All Time Low - It’s Still Nothing Personal
